This module provides utility functions for programmatically generating images 
using manually defined pixel data. It avoids the need for external image assets 
by constructing image data directly in Lua.

- create_image.ground_png() -> im.Image object
	Creates and returns a PNG image of a ground texture. The pixel data is 
	explicitly defined through RGB and alpha channel values to render the 
	final image.
- create_image.empty_png() -> im.Image object
	Creates and returns a transparent, 1x1 PNG image.
]]

